A plain text compression application for MikeOS.
Can reduced the size of text files by about 25%.

Syntax:
itc (action) (source) (destination)

  Compress - Compresses SOURCE file and saves to DESTINATION
  Decompress - Decompresses SOURCE files and save to original name
  Info - Presents information about a compressed file
  Help - Displays help screen

This program requires the MikeOS BASIC interpreter. 
It may not work on MikeOS derivatives or OS independent
versions of the MikeOS BASIC interpreter.

This program requires Hacklib, download it here:
http://

